metadata.name: UNCVRD 3095
metadata.description:
UNCVRD is the edition collection to the CVRD cars project.

To celebrate our CVRD launch we made this uncovered classic Mercedes as free to mint edition on a separate contract: UNCVRD by CVRD

Thank you all from the bottom of our heart. We want to get as many people as possible in our cars and become a part of it. This edition is for all of you.

All UNCVRD collectors will get an price advantage for our CVRD collection as follows (as long as it hasn't been sold):

Tier 2: 0.28 ETH instead of 0.38 ETH  
Tier 3: 0.40 ETH instead of 0.50 ETH

Just make an offer on the image of the CVRD series you like from Tier 2 and 3 here:  
https://opensea.io/collection/cvrd-by-karin-apollonia-mueller-and-peter-nitsch
